-- Pepsi Bottling Group second quarter profit rises
-- 
-- Tue Jul 8, 2008 6:58am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/08/businesspro-pepsibottling-results-dc-idUSWNAS039020080708

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Pepsi Bottling Group Inc PBG.N 
reported higher quarterly profit on Tuesday, helped by price 
increases in the U.S. and Canada. 

  The largest bottler of PepsiCo Inc ( PEP.N ) drinks said net 
income was $174 million, or 78 cents per share, in its fiscal 
second quarter, ended June 14, compared with $162 million, or 
70 cents per share, a year ago.  (Reporting by  Martinne Geller ; Editing by  Derek Caney )